  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-09-30",
    "date": "2022-02-14T15:23:09Z",
    "text": "Safety Enhancements for Communities Using Reasonable and Effective Firearm Storage Act or the SECURE Firearm Storage Act\n\nThis bill establishes security requirements for the business premises of a licensed firearms importer, manufacturer, or dealer.\n\nSpecifically, when the premises are closed for business, an importer, manufacturer, or dealer must secure the firearms inventory and securely store paper business records.\n\nA violator is subject to penalties\u2014a civil fine, suspension or revocation of a license, or both a civil fine and suspension or revocation of a license."
  },
